  Location: Section 9: Abstract
  Attack:   The proposed 'tensor interface' is not a novel construction; it is a rebranding of the well-established practice of using token-level log-probabilities (from which entropy is derived) for uncertainty quantification. This technique is foundational in the ML literature on model calibration and hallucination detection. The paper creates an artificial problem by defining a 'text-only' class that exclu...
